keywhiz.service.daos

Interface DAOFactory<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - DAO type produced by the factory
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AclDAO.AclDAOFactory, ClientDAO.ClientDAOFactory, GroupDAO.GroupDAOFactory, SecretDAO.SecretDAOFactory, SecretSeriesDAO.SecretSeriesDAOFactory

    public interface DAOFactory<T>
    DAO factory implement this interface to provide instances using different underlying database connections.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      T readonly()
      Returns DAO using a read-only database connection.
      T readwrite()
      Returns DAO using a read/write database connection.
      T using(org.jooq.Configuration configuration)
      Returns DAO using a supplied jOOQ configuration.

    • Method Detail

      • readwrite

        T readwrite()
        Returns DAO using a read/write database connection.

      • readonly

        T readonly()
        Returns DAO using a read-only database connection.

      • using

        T using(org.jooq.Configuration configuration)
        Returns DAO using a supplied jOOQ configuration. Useful for issuing queries on the same underlying transaction from a different DAO.
